name_original: Another World (itch) (Proksima, xNaxelx, danekpro12, KotekVCosmose, av1ty)
description: You are a scientist who worked on a parallel reality travel experiment. However, your experiment did not go according to plan and now you are in another world. You need to kill zombies while monitoring the anomalies that happen to your character. Good luck.
